# Canonical host: www -> apex (scrapeconvert.com).
#
# NOTE: Workers Static Assets `_redirects` only supports RELATIVE (path) sources.
# Host-based redirects are rejected at deploy time ("Only relative URLs are
# allowed" [code 100324]), so the www -> apex redirect CANNOT live in this file.
# It is handled by, in order of authority:
#   1. A zone-level Cloudflare Redirect Rule (authoritative; the only layer that
#      reliably covers static assets like /sitemap.xml). See docs/runbooks/cutover.md.
#   2. Astro middleware (src/middleware.ts) for SSR routes that reach the Worker.
#
# This file is intentionally rule-free (comments only) so the assets deploy
# validates. Add only RELATIVE-path redirects here if ever needed.
